# CHECK-NEXT:    thread list

# CHECK-FILTER: Hook: 2
# CHECK-FILTER-NEXT:  State: enabled
# CHECK-FILTER-NEXT:  AutoContinue on
# CHECK-FILTER-NEXT:  Commands: 
# CHECK-FILTER-NEXT:    script print('Hit stop hook')

# Get the threads going
continue

